HEADWORD: Casern
<hw>Ca"sern</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[F. <ets>caserne</ets>.]</ety> <def>A lodging for soldiers in garrison towns, usually near the rampart; barracks.</def>  <rj><au>Bescherelle.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
